skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Alexa can now read the latest heading lines from Eagle Eye as part as your daily briefing through the Alexa app. Headlines come directly from our website, eagleeyeauburn.com, and will soon feature weather and sports.

Setup is simple. Enable the Eagle Eye skill in your Alexa app and add us to your flash briefing!

War Eagle!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
